summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $38.42, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the 1910 general taxes on a part of lots 8, 11, 12, 13, and 14, B. W. John and C. H. Hanford's 5 Acre Lots, and a part of lot 7, section 23, township 24 north, range 4 east, W.M.
